Anson did a cake for me. Not a perfect cake but I love it. Fun activity to do at home during this #circuitbreaker ⁣
⁣
This is the first time Anson tried to decorate a cake. He decorated the mini cake that my sister-in-law baked. The cake is yummy. Swipe to see the bigger and nicer cake that she made. ⁣
⁣
We ordered our lunch from @jjthaicuisinesg Very delicious. I love their Tom yum soup. ⁣
⁣
Wishing all mummy Happy Mother's Day⁣
@hebe1304 @ayt89 @jingwenwu_nailsbywenz
⁣
⁣

#happymothersday #cake #homemade #cakedecorating #sgeat ⁣#sgkids #babygogosg #familylove⁣
